# Google Maps API Key for address autocomplete
# To enable address autocomplete:
# 1. Get a Google Maps API key from https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Enable the Places API for your project
# 3. Copy this file to .env and add your API key below
# 4. Restart the development server

# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Note: The app works without this - you can manually enter latitude/longitude
# The address autocomplete is an optional convenience feature
